<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-06-0194 </DOCNO><TEXT>If biomass is to become a primary alternative source of energy and chemicals,then an integrated biomass refinery incorporating complete feedstockutilization and producing a wide range of products must be adopted. Bio-HolDevelopments has taken the approach of fractionating biomass into hemicellulose,lignin, and cellulose. Isolating each of these components in high yieldswith high purities allows for conversion to the highest possible valueproducts. This article outlines the products the company has identifiedas having potential, classified according to the source biomass component.</TEXT></DOC>